title: AWS re:Invent 2025 - Utilizing AWS GenAI to deliver enterprise data modernization in CommBank-AIM416
title_cn: AWS re:Invent 2025 - 利用AWS生成式AI在联邦银行实现企业数据现代化-AIM416
abstract: Is this your first AWS re:Invent? Join this informational session to learn about selecting educational sessions that match your needs and learning style, navigating campus, accessibility options, what happens in Expo, available networking and activities, and much more. There will be time for Q&A to help you get the most out of your week. You can also meet other first-time attendees.
abstract_cn: 这是您第一次参加 AWS re:Invent 吗？加入这个信息介绍会，了解如何选择符合您需求和学习风格的教育课程、园区导航、无障碍选项、展览会的活动内容、可用的社交和活动机会等更多信息。会议将留出问答时间，帮助您充分利用这一周的时间。您还可以结识其他首次参会者。
